title: Iceland Car Registrations
description: Car Registrations in Iceland decreased to 1339 in October from 1691 in September of 2022. Car Registrations in Iceland averaged 1257.99  from 1995 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 5005  in May of 2017 and a record low of 77  in December of 2008. This page provides - Iceland Car Registrations - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Statistics Iceland
